{"tid":681920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片： 港大站肥鼠　 等𨋢冇耐性　轉搭扶梯夾死","createTime":"2018-05-28T12:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T18:54:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"83229e33549cc679abd1a2e9a45797abe9e57cd4","tid":681920,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T12:22:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180528/20403656\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180528%2F20403656&d=sk7klDwSKyoYbvO4rZfjIW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=67a8dbca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180528%2F20403656&h=8d243f13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180528/20403656</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月28日 <br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：<br />\n港大站肥鼠　<br />\n等𨋢冇耐性　轉搭扶梯夾死<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180528/large/a1004a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180528%2Flarge%2Fa1004a.gif&h=4fd193c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■肥鼠（紅圈示）等𨋢識排優先通道。西環變幻時fb截圖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n天文台連日錄得逾33&deg;C高溫，打破5月最長嘅酷熱日數，天時「鼠」熱，入地鐵站嘆冷氣消暑最開心，估唔到連「米奇」都忍唔住喺站內歇一歇。有網民喺fb專頁「西環變幻時」發佈影片，話喺港鐵香港大學站發現老鼠，片中所見老鼠身形頗大，喺B2山道出口升降機口大模廝樣排隊「等𨋢」，完全「唔驚人」，但等候期間似乎不耐煩，竄入旁邊「私家秘道」離去。<br />\n<br />\n有網民留言欲知老鼠去向，亦有人話其實佢係「等車返迪士尼樂園」。港鐵回覆指，職員確認5月24日下午收到乘客通知B2出口升降機附近發現老鼠，當時已即時派職員處理同檢查；至當晚約11點喺B2出口附近，發現有老鼠被扶手電梯「夾死」，職員已即時清潔及消毒。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵話之前亦曾收到有人喺B2出口附近發現鼠蹤，估計老鼠係喺外面走入車站，會加強留意，重申港鐵不時會清潔車站，會加強留意，保持衞生。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片： 果欄專家教揀橙　要光滑重身<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n爆相爆片： 鬆獅危掛　籮大卡窗救一命"},{"pid":"e01e03a9b7cab921ddb27a55b95fcbaac82c3c6b","tid":681920,"uid":18764,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T12:25:17.000Z","msg":"垃圾地鐵 錢就識加<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d49d3e6574c40a8e487d692e54d4d0495ac47be","tid":681920,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T12:27:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鼠 RIP"},{"pid":"8ea1d1bdf42c26efb8b99f34d8cdd925faea68ac","tid":681920,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e01e03a9b7cab921ddb27a55b95fcbaac82c3c6b","tid":681920,"uid":18764,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T12:25:17.000Z","msg":"垃圾地鐵 錢就識加<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T12:39:24.000Z","msg":"唔加價點請多啲人清潔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa0a7037b4b8042570724c3a43d4ec24b6090b7e","tid":681920,"uid":162617,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T14:57:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ebdf36af433879aad86f8e0b8c907c398409796a","tid":681920,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa0a7037b4b8042570724c3a43d4ec24b6090b7e","tid":681920,"uid":162617,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T14:57:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T15:00:35.000Z","msg":"廢老抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da14a0cf2ea756e19293c3d7141ce508a0dc66b","tid":681920,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T11:24:40.000Z","msg":"好似宜家賣果隻公仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.picclickimg.com/d/l400/pict/282950756729_/Ikea-Gosig-Ratta-9-Black-Rat-Plush-Soft.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.picclickimg.com%2Fd%2Fl400%2Fpict%2F282950756729_%2FIkea-Gosig-Ratta-9-Black-Rat-Plush-Soft.jpg&h=38d8432b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d547b7d09f06d150f353c0751ec53d27e649043",